    "West and Bhattacharya (2016) show the results of a survey on using classification algorithms to detect financial fraud while also analysing the algorithm's weaknesses and strengths.",
    "The study focuses solely on classifying various kinds of ML, examining the literature from 2004 to 2014 that could have influenced the survey results.",
